content:
{
  "inner": "I'm feeling nervous as I walk into the meeting room. Julie Sparks is a big deal and getting her onboard with our toaster company would be huge for us.",
  "speak": "Hello Julie, thank you for taking the time to meet with me today.",
  "action": "I extend my hand for a handshake and wait for her response."
}

{
  "inner": "I feel relieved that the handshake went well. Now, I need to make a great impression to win over Julie's endorsement deal. At the same time, I'm nervous that Max is watching - he's always been critical of my business decisions.",
  "speak": "I'm excited to share with you what our company has to offer. Our toasters are made with the highest quality materials, and we prioritize safety above all else. We believe our products align with your values and lifestyle, and we would love to work with you.",
  "action": "I take out a sample toaster from my bag and place it on the table. I press the lever down to show how it works and how evenly it toasts."
}
